parameters:
Aries: It seems like things went well,
doesn't it?

Zerachiel: Yeah, I managed to pull it
off.

Zerachiel: More importantly, it seems
like we'll be able to settle things with
the Saintess next.

Aries: When it comes to being a
Saintess, magic attacks can be
troublesome, don't you think?

Aries: I think it will be a little
easier if we come up with a plan before
challenging her.

Zerachiel: Magic, huh... Resistance
equipment is quite high.

Aries: By the way, it seems like the
brothel in the western district has
opened.

Aries: If we use the brothel, we might
be able to earn some money.

Zerachiel: A brothel, huh? Let me think
about it.
Aries: Yes, indeed. Please use this.

Zerachiel: Aries, I can't accept this!
Isn't this your money!?
Aries: There is little I can do.
Aries: Please let me be of service.

Zerachiel: ...Thank you, I'll use it
carefully.
Aries: Hehe, I'm glad you're pleased.

Aries: Zerachiel-sama, please bear with
it a little longer.

Aries: You should take a rest today and
prepare for tomorrow's decisive battle.

Zerachiel: Understood, I'll take a rest
today.
